c/nine-inch-nails-doechii-lola-young-more-join-stacked-roskilde-2025-3832591">九英寸的指甲，doechii，lola Young，湿腿和更多加入的Roskilde 2025阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nine-Inch-Nails-Doechii-Lola-Young-and-Wet-Leg.-Credit-R.-Diamond-Rebecca-Sapp-Matt-Jelonek-and-Roberto-Ricciuti-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="九英寸的指甲，doechii，萝拉·杨和湿腿。图片来源：R。Diamond，Rebecca Sapp，Matt Jelonek和Roberto Ricciuti通过Getty" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nine-Inch-Nails-Doechii-Lola-Young-and-Wet-Leg.-Credit-R.-Diamond-Rebecca-Sapp-Matt-Jelonek-and-Roberto-Ricciuti-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nine-Inch-Nails-Doechii-Lola-Young-and-Wet-Leg.-Credit-R.-Diamond-Rebecca-Sapp-Matt-Jelonek-and-Roberto-Ricciuti-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nine-Inch-Nails-Doechii-Lola-Young-and-Wet-Leg.-Credit-R.-Diamond-Rebecca-Sapp-Matt-Jelonek-and-Roberto-Ricciuti-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nine-Inch-Nails-Doechii-Lola-Young-and-Wet-Leg.-Credit-R.-Diamond-Rebecca-Sapp-Matt-Jelonek-and-Roberto-Ricciuti-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nine-Inch-Nails-Doechii-Lola-Young-and-Wet-Leg.-Credit-R.-Diamond-Rebecca-Sapp-Matt-Jelonek-and-Roberto-Ricciuti-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Nine-Inch-Nails-Doechii-Lola-Young-and-Wet-Leg.-Credit-R.-Diamond-Rebecca-Sapp-Matt-Jelonek-and-Roberto-Ricciuti-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Nine-Inch-Nails">九英寸的指甲</a>， <a href="/artists/Doechii">Doechii</a> ， <a href="/artists/Lola-Young">Lola Young</a> ，<a href="/artists/Wet-Leg">湿腿</a>等被宣布为今年<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/roskilde-festival">Roskilde Festival</a>的第三波表演者。</p><p>丹麦非营利节2025年的分期付款将于6月28日至7月5日之间举行，标志着第53版。您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Froskilde-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F1409275" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问这里购买门票。</a></p><p> Other acts added to the line-up include <a href="/artists/Beabadoobee">Beabadoobee</a> , <a href="/artists/Schoolboy-Q">Schoolboy Q</a> , <a href="/artists/Shaboozey">Shaboozey</a> , <a href="/artists/Lucy-Dacus">Lucy Dacus</a> , Ca7riel &amp; Paco Amoroso, This Is Lorelei, Alabaster DePlume, Yeule, Fabiana Palladino, Akriila, D1MA, 4am Kru, Alabaster Deplume, Annahstasia, Arushi Jain ，身体肉，沙发荡妇，Fabiana Palladino，Jako Maron，Kassa整体，美国职棒大联盟DJZ，Moin，Neckbreakker，Nídia和Valentina，Paydar，Soleima和Yeule。</p><p>将在不久的将来宣布更多行为。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFXQproMDIy/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1