//www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beth-gibbons">Beth Gibbons</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arca">Arca</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/faye-webster">Faye Webster</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/magdalena-bay">Magdalena Bay</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fat-dog">Fat Dog</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/geordie-greep">Geordie Greep</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/i-jordan">I。Jordan</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Wisp">Wisp</a>和Snow Strippers。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roskilde-festival-2025-olivia-rodrigo-deftones-jamie-xx-more-buy-tickets-3816741">去年11月宣布了第二波阵容</a>，并以<a href="/artists/Olivia-Rodrigo">Olivia Rodrigo</a> ， <a href="/artists/Deftones">Deftones</a> ， <a href="/artists/Jamie-xx">Jamie XX</a> ， <a href="/artists/Charli-XCX">Charli XCX</a> ， <a href="/artists/Lambrini-Girls">Lambrini Girls</a> ， <a href="/artists/A-G-Cook">Ag Cook</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mary-wallopers">Ag Wallopers</a> ，Artigeardit，Artigeardit， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/saint-levant">Saint Levant</a> ，Saint Levant，Anoushka Shankar，Flock，Flock Shankar，Flock，Flock，Flock，Flock，Flock，Flock，Flock，Flock，Flock，Flock，Flock，弗洛克，弗洛弗里尼XC，弗洛弗·库克，弗洛弗·库克，弗洛普斯， ，Nala Sinephro和Hitech。</p><p> Last year, Roskilde saw <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-to-headline-roskilde-festival-2024-3533053">Foo Fighters</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roskilde-festival-2024-doja-cat-janes-addiction-and-more-join-line-up-3576696">Doja Cat</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skrillex">Skrillex</a> headline the festival, with <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pj-harvey-first-headliner-roskilde-festival-2024-line-up-buy-tickets-3526732">PJ Harvey</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/21-savage">21 Savage</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pinkpantheress">PinkPantheress</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janes-addiction">Jane&#39;s Addiction</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-spice">Ice Spice</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/khruangbin">Khruangbin</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-hus">J Hus</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-carter-and-the-rattlesnakes">Frank Carter &amp; The Rattlesnakes</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/romy">Romy</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aurora">Aurora</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondshell">Blondshell</a>也在阵容中进行了特色。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nine-inch-nails-doechii-lola-young-more-join-stacked-roskilde-2025-3832591">九英寸的指甲，doechii，lola Young，湿腿和更多加入的Roskilde 2025阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
